About Us
/$
$
Lakeside Mobile Manor is a retirement community (55 plus) with permanent mobile home sites as well as R.V. sites, sitting on a four acre lake with plenty of trees around the community that provides lots of shade.  You can enjoy a varity of wildlife right from the privacy of your own home.​
A great retirement community for those active seniors who would like to travel and spend some quality time in a nice campground or settle into a permenant home in a mobile home park.  A Florida RV Park is just the place for you
/$
$
/$
$
Meet the managers
Ken and Hope are the park managers.
Hello, just a few words to share my thoughts about Lakeside Mobile Manor.
My wife and I have both managed other parks before coming to Lakeside.
Looking back over the other places we have been, I think we have found our little place in paradise.
The atmosphere is so nice and peaceful, and the residents are some of the nicest people you could ever meet.  we have been managing Lakeside Mobile Manor for 8 years, and plan to be here for years to come.  In summary, I finally found the pot of gold at the end of the rainbow.
Ken
Hi there!  I would like to share some of my thoughts and feelings on Lakeside Mobile Manor.  We both love this park and the peacefulness and quietness.  We enjoy setting in screen room watching all the different birds, ducks and even a gator now and then.  You couldnt ask for nicer residents.  As my husband has said we found the pot of gold and we plan on staying for years to come.
Hope

Living the life you deserve
The residents here at Lakeside are enjoying the life they have worked so hard to have.
Some still like to travel back north during the summer months to be with family, and others have decided to stay year round.
With our residents in mind, we have a clubhouse for their enjoyment.
Pitch-in dinners, karaoke, parties, horse shoe pits, and Saturday morning coffee & donuts.
﻿

Meet the events coordinators
Judy T, Judy W, Kelly L, and Lou T, are resident event coordinators.
Some of the things we do here at Lakeside include:
Coffee and donuts on Saturday mornings.
Pot Luck Dinners on the first and third Mondays.
Thanksgiving, Christmas, Easter, and St Patrick's Day dinners.
(park owner furnishes the meat)
Christmas Party.
Bicycling for everyone (two and three wheel)
There are always building or repair projects going on that brings out skillful willing help.
It is just a small home town park where everyone knows everyone else, and will pitch in when help is needed.  And we have fun together.
